data.description: Welcome to 649 Pavia Loop, a stunning townhome located in the sought-after gated community of Fountain Parke at Lake Mary. This meticulously well-maintained 4 bedroom 3-and-a-half bath home offers over 2000 square feet of living space, providing ample room for your family’s comfort and lifestyle. When entering this 3-level home you are greeted by beautiful 18” tile, fresh paint, soaring high ceilings, and a living space that creates a welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen is a stand-out feature, boasting elegant granite counter tops, 42” cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and an updated microwave. On the next level of the home, you’ll find the spacious master suite and a master bath featuring dual vanities, a walk-in closet, and a walk-in shower with a frameless glass enclosure, adding a touch of convenience and luxury to your daily routine. There are also 2 additional bedrooms on the second floor and a bathroom complete with a shower and tub combo. The original owners of this pet-free home have also updated the washing machine & dryer (2021), Ac (2019) and replaced the carpet (2022). This home also offers Cat 5E cable throughout the entire home, a 2-car garage, a water softener/filtration system, new exterior paint and stucco, a second-floor balcony for relaxation, and a ground-level space complete with a private bathroom, and a walk-in closet that would be ideal for a home office or 4th bedroom. The community of Fountain Parke at Lake Mary is conveniently located in the heart of Lake Mary, renowned for its top-rated schools, dining, entertainment, and recreational opportunities. Residents of the community will also enjoy a community pool, clubhouse, fitness center, and tennis courts. The HOA also takes care of all the yard and exterior maintenance for the residents. If you’re a busy family or professional looking for a low-maintenance lifestyle this is the home for you. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the elegance of 649 Pavia Loop, Lake Mary.
